PURPOSE: We aimed to evaluate the effects of preoperative pulmonary hypertension 
(PH) on early and long term results in patients undergoing coronary bypass 
surgery and the effects of coronary bypass surgery on PH.
METHODS: Among 2325 patients who underwent elective isolated coronary artery 
bypass surgery between March 2003 and March 2012, 287 patients with high 
