Point-of-care CD4 testing to inform selection of antiretroviral medications in 
south african antenatal clinics: a cost-effectiveness analysis.

Ciaranello AL(1), Myer L(2), Kelly K(3), Christensen S(3), Daskilewicz K(2), 
Doherty K(3), Bekker LG(4), Hou T(5), Wood R(4), Francke JA(3), Wools-Kaloustian 
